BoolBornNative
/ `set %b% = true` lands %b% with type "bool" — the value is bool.@this, not a
/ raw CLR bool mid-flight. Same for false. JSON True/False arms emit the wrapper.
- set %b% = true
- assert %b.Type.Name% equals "bool"
- assert %b% equals true
- set %c% = false
- assert %c.Type.Name% equals "bool"
- assert %c% equals false
